name: Cloud Computing
description:
This composite image is about contrasts—the non-tech crumbling remains of a 100+ year-old structure surrounding a cutting-edge motherboard. Within the motherboard I embedded a circular window and superimposed an image of the sky from Arizona—gives new meaning to the idea of cloud computing. 


About the View Portal
The wall that frames the image is all that remains of a building in a ghost town in Nevada. The town is defunct; the only life forms other than tourists are the resident rattlesnakes.
